# Anti-pollution: experiments/ contains exploratory work that
# should NOT be committed to master. Whitelist explicitly the
# sandboxes that need tracking (typically those linked to
# specific feature branches or simulations).
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
experiments/
